Class TdApi.Authorization

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drinkless.td.libcore.telegram.TdApi.TLObject

  • Enclosing class:
    TdApi

    public static class TdApi.Authorization
extends TdApi.TLObject
    Contains information about one authorization in some application used by the user.
